    "created_at": "2015-01-26T05:16:19Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-01-26T05:16:19Z",
    "body": "> Under normal circumstances, the only requirement is that \"Drop\" is able to correctly handle any of the intermediate states resulting from a panic\n\nWhy is that the case? Many destructors can reference the type that's in an invalid state while the thread is unwinding.\n",
