    "created_at": "2015-01-26T08:31:35Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-01-26T08:31:35Z",
    "body": "This was an explicit design decision of poisoning mutexes and being able to access the poisoned data as the unsafety here is **not** memory unsafety unless there is other already-`unsafe` code in play (which is the responsibility of the `unsafe` code, not poisoning).\n\nIssues like this to change the standard library APIs [now belong](http://discuss.rust-lang.org/t/issue-categorization-changes/1417) in the RFC repo as well.\n",
    "author_association": "MEMBER",
